<div class="row faq">
  <div class="col-sm-9">
    <h1>Regional Chapters</h1>

    <div class="row" id="devcon-chapters">
      <div class="col-sm-12">
        <p>Being a fast growing community, DevCon already has local chapters in <strong>Cebu</strong>, <strong>Davao</strong> and <strong>Cagayan de Oro (CDO)</strong>. Each chapter has its own set of events and a steering committee. Here are the current chapter heads:</p>
        <div class="row officer">
          <div class="col-sm-12 profile">
            <h3><span class="caps">Paul John Parreño</span>, DevCon Bai! (Cebu) Chapter Head</h3>
            <p class="twitter-handle"><a href="http://twitter.com/pjparreno" target="_blank">@pjparreno</a></p>
            <p><%= image_tag "faq/pj.jpg", :alt => "PJ", :class => "profile-pic pull-left" %> Paul is a Mobile Applications Developer at Arcanys Inc, Mobile Technology Enthusiast, University Instructor at University of San Carlos, and a Gaming Enthusiast. He also particularly interested in open source technology that drives mobile applications development, open-source game development and promoting the technological growth in the Philippines. Learn more about him on his <a href="http://www.linkedin.com/pub/paul-john-parreno/58/112/887">LinkedIn profile</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row officer">
          <div class="col-sm-12 profile">
            <h3><span class="caps">Cris John Tagupa</span>, DevCon Cagayan de Oro Chapter Head</h3>
            <p class="twitter-handle"><a href="https://twitter.com/cjtagupa" target="_blank">@cjtagupa</a></p>
            <p><%= image_tag "faq/devcon-cris.jpg", :alt => "Cris", :class => "profile-pic pull-left" %> Cris is a Web Developer at Force12 Media, Inc. He holds a Bachelor’s degree in Information Technology, graduating Magna cum Laude from Liceo de Cagayan University. He considers himself as very lucky to be able to work on something that he loves so much. Code is Poetry.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row officer">
          <div class="col-sm-12 profile">
            <h3><span class="caps">Jaymar Somosot</span>, DevCon Davao Chapter Head</h3>
            <p class="twitter-handle"><a href="http://twitter.com/strangershots" target="_blank">@strangershots</a></p>
            <p><%= image_tag "faq/js.jpg", :alt => "Jay", :class => "profile-pic pull-left" %> Jay is an autodidact who was introduced to DevCon in 2011 and has been a passionate volunteer since. His interest is on Open Source technology, DevOps, Cloud Computing and other SysAdmin related stuffs. He is currently pursuing his bachelor's degree while doing freelance jobs for local and international companies.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="apply-local-chapter">To apply for a local chapter, feel free to email our Executive Director via <a href="mailto:haifa@devcon.ph">haifa@devcon.ph</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

